<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 18:09:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列全国各地抗议，人质家属称内塔尼亚胡选择升级而不是达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-say-pm-chose-escalation-over-deal/00000191-18f8-d116-a9db-dcfda6d00000</link><description>全国各地都在举行要求达成人质协议的抗议活动，而由于担心伊朗或其代理人发动袭击，通常每周举行的反政府抗议活动被取消</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 16:42:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-say-pm-chose-escalation-over-deal/00000191-18f8-d116-a9db-dcfda6d00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第302天：人质家属称内塔尼亚胡选择升级而不是达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-302-mossad-shin-bet-chief-travel-to-egypt-and-return/00000191-1913-db97-a7df-fdfb8d3f0000</link><description>以色列谈判小组高级成员告诉《国土报》，以色列国防部长认为总理内塔尼亚胡对释放人质/停火协议不感兴趣 ■ 据报道，瑞典关闭了驻贝鲁特的贝鲁特大使馆，美国、英国敦促黎巴嫩国民尽快离开该国■ 以色列摩萨德和辛贝特领导人前往埃及并返回以色列继续停战谈判 ■ 战争开始 302 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 16:35:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-302-mossad-shin-bet-chief-travel-to-egypt-and-return/00000191-1913-db97-a7df-fdfb8d3f0000</guid></item><item><title>由于地区紧张局势和价格飙升，这些航空公司削减了飞往以色列的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/these-are-the-airlines-cutting-flights-to-israel-as-regional-tensions-and-prices-skyrocket/00000191-1457-db7e-a99d-1edf0f6b0000</link><description>到目前为止，所有为以色列服务的美国航空公司以及几家欧洲航空公司都已暂停航班。以色列旗舰航空公司以色列航空维持正常航班，但票价却飙升</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 16:26:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/these-are-the-airlines-cutting-flights-to-israel-as-regional-tensions-and-prices-skyrocket/00000191-1457-db7e-a99d-1edf0f6b0000</guid></item><item><title>官员警告称，恐怖组织利用阿拉伯犯罪组织袭击以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/arab-crime-organizations-being-used-by-terror-groups-to-attack-israel-officials-warn/00000191-18ad-d4cf-afb5-5cfdf97d0000</link><description>以色列国防官员警告部长们，“有组织犯罪对国家安全构成战略威胁”，并警告外国恐怖组织已经试图利用以色列境内的犯罪组织实施袭击。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 15:39:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/arab-crime-organizations-being-used-by-terror-groups-to-attack-israel-officials-warn/00000191-18ad-d4cf-afb5-5cfdf97d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人阿尔乔姆·多尔戈皮亚特在巴黎奥运会体操自由体操决赛中获得银牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/london-2012/olympics-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-gymnast-artem-dolgopyat-clinches-silver-medal-at-paris-olympics-gymnastics-final/00000191-188d-dd1b-a9f5-ff8d36ec0000</link><description>多尔戈皮亚特的胜利使以色列的奥运奖牌总数达到 19 枚，其中 6 枚是在 2024 年巴黎奥运会上获得的</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 14:27:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/london-2012/olympics-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-gymnast-artem-dolgopyat-clinches-silver-medal-at-paris-olympics-gymnastics-final/00000191-188d-dd1b-a9f5-ff8d36ec0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，以色列人质埃坦·利维 (Eitan Levy) 的家人公布了加沙人踢打、虐待他身体的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/family-of-israeli-hostage-eitan-levy-release-footage-of-gazans-abusing-his-body-on-oct-7/00000191-186a-d053-a7ff-5bfee3bd0000</link><description>利维于 10 月 7 日被杀，他的尸体被运往加沙。视频显示，利维的尸体在一辆汽车的敞开的后备箱中，后来躺在地上，而加沙人则对其拳打脚踢。 Levy是一名53岁的出租车司机，10月7日在载着一名乘客前往加沙边境时被杀</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 14:10:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/family-of-israeli-hostage-eitan-levy-release-footage-of-gazans-abusing-his-body-on-oct-7/00000191-186a-d053-a7ff-5bfee3bd0000</guid></item><item><title>《国土报》摄影师拍摄的以色列一周</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-week-in-pictures/00000191-1865-dd1b-a9f5-ff6d46a00000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 13:56:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-week-in-pictures/00000191-1865-dd1b-a9f5-ff6d46a00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队袭击约旦河西岸图尔卡尔姆；巴勒斯坦人报告九人死亡，其中包括哈马斯指挥官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/israeli-army-strikes-west-bank-palestinians-report-nine-dead-including-hamas-commander/00000191-17a4-df57-afd7-f7b633bd0000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，他们使用无人机在图尔卡尔姆击落了一辆载有恐怖分子的车辆，并声称车内人员正在前往发动袭击的路上。军队第二次袭击图尔卡姆，目击者称两次袭击造成九人死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 13:38:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/israeli-army-strikes-west-bank-palestinians-report-nine-dead-including-hamas-commander/00000191-17a4-df57-afd7-f7b633bd0000</guid></item><item><title>汤姆·鲁文尼 (Tom Reuveni) 夺得金牌，莎朗·坎特 (Sharon Kantor) 夺得银牌；以色列奖牌数增至五枚，创本届奥运会历史最高奖牌数</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sharon-kantor-wins-olympic-silver-tom-reuveni-guarantees-medal-at-semi-finals/00000191-181a-d68e-a79b-5b9fdb110000</link><description>21 岁的坎特 (Kantor) 在女子组比赛中获得银牌后不久，23 岁的鲁文尼 (Reuveni) 在 IQFoil 组别中赢得了金牌。这些奖牌使以色列的奥运奖牌总数达到 18 枚，其中 5 枚是在 2024 年巴黎奥运会上获得的</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 12:10:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sharon-kantor-wins-olympic-silver-tom-reuveni-guarantees-medal-at-semi-finals/00000191-181a-d68e-a79b-5b9fdb110000</guid></item><item><title>报告：哈尼亚遇刺后希腊“高度戒备”针对以色列目标的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-03/ty-article/greece-on-high-alert-for-attack-against-israeli-targets-after-haniyeh-assassination/00000191-1754-d68e-a79b-5fd5abee0000</link><description>据希腊《Kathimerini》报纸报道，希腊当局正在与外国情报机构联系，了解有关雅典以色列或犹太人目标遭受袭击的威胁加剧的报道。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 10:18:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-08-03/ty-article/greece-on-high-alert-for-attack-against-israeli-targets-after-haniyeh-assassination/00000191-1754-d68e-a79b-5fd5abee0000</guid></item><item><title>报道：以色列摩萨德雇佣伊朗特工在哈马斯头目哈尼亚的房间里放置炸药</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/report-israels-mossad-hired-iranian-agents-to-plant-explosives-in-hamas-chiefs-room/00000191-16fa-db7e-a99d-1efa23980000</link><description>伊朗消息人士告诉《每日电讯报》，负责高级官员安全的革命卫队特工在哈马斯领导人被杀的德黑兰宾馆的另外两个房间里安放了爆炸装置</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 07:41:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/report-israels-mossad-hired-iranian-agents-to-plant-explosives-in-hamas-chiefs-room/00000191-16fa-db7e-a99d-1efa23980000</guid></item><item><title>英国和美国鼓励公民尽快离开黎巴嫩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article-live/haniyeh-killing-carried-out-by-mossad-hired-iranian-agents-u-s-moves-warships-to-mideast/00000191-155d-dba6-a59d-175f1a530000</link><description>伊朗：将在“适当的时间、地点和方式”对哈马斯头目被杀进行“严厉”的报复 ■ 报告：17 岁儿童在黎巴嫩南部的袭击中丧生 ■ 据哈马斯媒体报道，以色列的袭击导致加沙学校 15 人死亡办公室 ■ 以色列定居者焚烧约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦农田 ■ 巴勒斯坦人报告称，约旦河西岸图尔卡姆的袭击造成 9 人死亡 ■ 美国国防部长命令海军巡洋舰和驱逐舰前往中东</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 01:35:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article-live/haniyeh-killing-carried-out-by-mossad-hired-iranian-agents-u-s-moves-warships-to-mideast/00000191-155d-dba6-a59d-175f1a530000</guid></item><item><title>战争会迎来以色列的救赎吗？弥赛亚狂热不仅受到宗教狂热分子的欢迎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/war-will-usher-in-israels-redemption-messianic-fervor-gains-popularity-beyond-fanatics/00000191-14c4-df57-afd7-f6f6e4bb0000</link><description>灾难是世界末日预言传播者的沃土</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 23:55:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/war-will-usher-in-israels-redemption-messianic-fervor-gains-popularity-beyond-fanatics/00000191-14c4-df57-afd7-f6f6e4bb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队袭击了两个巴勒斯坦村庄，一小时内杀死了两人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-troops-raided-two-palestinian-villages-and-killed-two-men-within-an-hour/00000191-14f7-d4cf-afb5-5cf715340000</link><description>士兵们杀害了一名巴勒斯坦社会工作者，这名社会工作者恳求他们让一辆载着一名临产妇女的救护车通过。他们向死者家发射催泪瓦斯，还杀死了另一名投掷石块的男子</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 22:53:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-troops-raided-two-palestinian-villages-and-killed-two-men-within-an-hour/00000191-14f7-d4cf-afb5-5cf715340000</guid></item><item><title>越来越多的耶路撒冷保安人员是巴勒斯坦人。这就是为什么这是一个充满希望的发展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/many-jerusalem-security-guards-are-palestinian-heres-why-thats-a-hopeful-development/00000191-143b-d116-a9db-dc7f45130000</link><description>商场和停车场的巴勒斯坦保安只是一个巨大现象的冰山一角：耶路撒冷的巴勒斯坦居民融入以色列当地社会</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 20:23:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/many-jerusalem-security-guards-are-palestinian-heres-why-thats-a-hopeful-development/00000191-143b-d116-a9db-dc7f45130000</guid></item><item><title>高级官员表示，以色列国防部长认为内塔尼亚胡对加沙协议不感兴趣</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/israeli-defense-chiefs-believe-netanyahu-isnt-interested-in-gaza-deal-top-official-says/00000191-14a0-d4cf-afb5-5cf5a8aa0000</link><description>以色列谈判小组的高级成员描述了内塔尼亚胡和高级国防官员之间在人质交易上的“分歧”；电视报道援引了总理指责他们太“软弱”的激烈交锋</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 20:15:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/israeli-defense-chiefs-believe-netanyahu-isnt-interested-in-gaza-deal-top-official-says/00000191-14a0-d4cf-afb5-5cf5a8aa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队如何播下 10 月 7 日灾难的种子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-israels-army-sowed-the-seeds-of-its-october-7-disaster/00000191-13ba-db7e-a99d-1fba4cca0000</link><description>双桅船。盖伊·哈祖特 (Guy Hazoot) 将军的新书强调了 10 月 7 日哈马斯的傲慢和自满。同样的缺点是否会在与真主党或伊朗的更广泛战争中阻碍以色列？</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 18:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-israels-army-sowed-the-seeds-of-its-october-7-disaster/00000191-13ba-db7e-a99d-1fba4cca0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第301天：美国官员称伊朗可能使用代理人进行报复性攻击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-301-u-s-officials-say-iran-may-use-proxies-in-retaliation-attack/00000191-13dc-d5cd-abfd-b7dec2cf0000</link><description>美国官员：伊朗可能利用代理人攻击美军和以色列目标 ■ 真主党主席誓言对高级指挥官被杀做出回应 ■ 以色列国防军称在加沙南部杀害了巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战组织高级成员 ■ 拜登与内塔尼亚胡就支持以色列的新防御性军事部署进行了交谈■ 战争开始 301 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 17:02:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-301-u-s-officials-say-iran-may-use-proxies-in-retaliation-attack/00000191-13dc-d5cd-abfd-b7dec2cf0000</guid></item><item><title>利库德集团呼吁处决以色列资深记者内胡姆·巴尼亚，因为他开玩笑说袭击了内塔尼亚胡的空飞机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/likud-mk-calls-to-execute-journalist-over-joke-about-striking-netanyahus-empty-plane/00000191-13e8-dcc9-a1d3-b7fc85e20000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡政党的塔利·戈特利夫因伊朗在飞机停放且空无一人时瞄准这架飞机的笑话而威胁记者。自收购以来，“锡安之翼”就象征着奢华、脱离公众和滥用资金</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 16:56:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/likud-mk-calls-to-execute-journalist-over-joke-about-striking-netanyahus-empty-plane/00000191-13e8-dcc9-a1d3-b7fc85e20000</guid></item><item><title>诺亚·阿加玛尼会与有关她被囚禁的漫画书背后的日本艺术家见面吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/will-noa-argamani-meet-japanese-artist-behind-manga-book-on-her-captivity/00000191-0e58-d87c-a7d5-9e7a6ae90000</link><description>加沙将不可避免地加入动漫节，即使只是非正式的。此外，传奇歌手 Chava Alberstein 发布了一首纪念战争 300 天的歌曲，并举办了一场新展览，探索 Maskit 时装屋的历史</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 16:31:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/will-noa-argamani-meet-japanese-artist-behind-manga-book-on-her-captivity/00000191-0e58-d87c-a7d5-9e7a6ae90000</guid></item></channel></rss>